\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub If any of you lacks wisdom, you should ask God,\'a0who gives generously to all without finding fault, and it will be given to you.\'a0
\f1\b\fs20 \super 6\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But when you ask, you must believe and not doubt,\'a0because the one who doubts is like a wave of the sea, blown and tossed by the wind.\'a0
\f1\b\fs20 \super 7\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub That person should not expect to receive anything from the Lord.\'a0
\f1\b\fs20 \super 8\'a0
